creator: Ducatus Global
descriptionHtml:
Ducatus Wallet for Android. Manage your funds.
Now supporting Bitcoin, Bitcoin Cash and Ethereum.

The Ducatus wallet provides safe and easy access to your Ducatus coins. Ducatus is a fully decentralised cryptocurrency which works just like Bitcoin but faster! Your wallet can be used to send coins to anywhere in the world and to buy items from the luxury collection in the online Ducatus store as well as from a growing number of other participating merchant partners.
descriptionShort: Manage your funds. Now supporting Bitcoin, Bitcoin Cash and Ethereum.
